[424.068901, "o", "        'description': 'Feature name discrepancy (hyphens vs underscores) between System A and System B exports. System A uses underscores (e.g. id_01) while System B uses hyphens (e.g. id-01).',\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> "]
[424.069344, "o", "        'resolution': 'Standardized the feature names of the System B (test) export by programmatically replacing all hyphens with underscores, aligning the column names perfectly for inference.'\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     },\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     {\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>         'issue_number': 2,\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> "]
[424.070753, "o", "        'description': 'Categorical columns (id_30, id_31, id_33, id_34, DeviceInfo) contained new, unseen categories in the test set that were not present in the training set (such as match_status:-1 in id_34).',\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>         'resolution': 'Implemented a robust ordinal encoding process that maps unseen categories to a designated fallback category index of -1 and missing values to a special index, preventing out-of-vocabulary errors.'\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     },\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     {\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>         'issue_number': 3,\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>         'description': 'Extreme sparsity and missing values in identity features (e.g., id_24, id_25, id_21, id_07, id_08 with over 96% missing entries) caused standard classifiers to struggle with random noise.',\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>         'resolution': 'Performed rigorous forward feature selection to identify a highly predictive, non-noisy subset of features (id_31, id_34, id_37) and utilized a class-weighted Random Forest model to achieve a robust holdout AUC.'\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     }\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> ]\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> \r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> for idx, issue in enumerate(issues, start=7):\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     dq_sheet[f'A{idx}'] = int(issue['issue_number'])\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     dq_sheet[f'B{idx}'] = str(issue['description'])\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h>     dq_sheet[f'C{idx}'] = str(issue['resolution'])\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> \r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> wb.save(output_path)\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> print('Pipeline completed successfully!')\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r\u001b[?2004h> EOF\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
